#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn4.8"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn4.8:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 4 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 4 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn4.8:0.2"
msgid "1. Paṭhamavagga "
msgstr "1. Life Span "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 8. Nandatisutta → nandanasuttaṃ (s1-3) | nandanaṃ (pts1)
msgctxt "sn4.8:0.3"
msgid "8. Nandatisutta "
msgstr "8. Delighting "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p><span class="evam">
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn4.8:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—"
msgstr "So I have heard. "

#. HTML: </span>
msgctxt "sn4.8:1.2"
msgid "ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn4.8:1.3"
msgid "Atha kho māro pāpimā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavato santike imaṃ gāthaṃ abhāsi: "
msgstr "Then Māra the Wicked went up to the Buddha and recited this verse in the Buddha’s presence: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: pts1ed1.108, pts2ed1.241, sc2
msgctxt "sn4.8:2.1"
msgid "“Nandati puttehi puttimā, "
msgstr "“Your children bring you delight! "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn4.8:2.2"
msgid "Gomā gobhi tatheva nandati; "
msgstr "Your cattle also bring you delight! "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn4.8:2.3"
msgid "Upadhīhi narassa nandanā, "
msgstr "For attachments are a man’s delight; "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn4.8:2.4"
msgid "Na hi so nandati yo nirūpadhī”ti. "
msgstr "without attachments there’s no delight.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn4.8:3.1"
msgid "“Socati puttehi puttimā, "
msgstr "“Your children bring you sorrow. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn4.8:3.2"
msgid "Gomā gobhi tatheva socati; "
msgstr "Your cattle also bring you sorrow. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn4.8:3.3"
msgid "Upadhīhi narassa socanā, "
msgstr "For attachments are a man’s sorrow; "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn4.8:3.4"
msgid "Na hi so socati yo nirūpadhī”ti. "
msgstr "without attachments there are no sorrows.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "sn4.8:4.1"
msgid "Atha kho māro pāpimā “jānāti maṃ bhagavā, jānāti maṃ sugato”ti dukkhī dummano tatthevantaradhāyīti. "
msgstr "Then Māra the Wicked, thinking, “The Buddha knows me! The Holy One knows me!” miserable and sad, vanished right there."

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
